CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, January 20, 1962, pg. A14 reads:"It's "Projection '62" - A distinguished panel of ten top-flight correspondents of the National Broadcasting Co. discuss foreign policy during a symposium sponsored by the Foreign Policy Association at the Hotel Hilton, last Thursday night...-Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Men and women seated at numbered banquet tables, including woman wearing dark polka dot dress in center, in Hilton Hotel for Foreign Policy Association symposium
